[
  {
    "content_id": 694426,
    "reference_id": 18840,
    "title": "猶大書 1:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "65001001",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>猶大（Jude或Judas）是希伯來名字「猶大」（Judah）的希臘文版本。這是一個常見的名字。這位猶大是雅各的弟兄，雅各也是耶穌的弟兄（見<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"Jude_BookIntro_Filament\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotes\">猶大書簡介</span>，「作者」）。</p></li><li><p><em>耶穌基督的僕人</em>：猶大指出他在生命的各個層面都跟隨耶穌。這個稱呼也彰顯了其榮耀。舊約聖經中的重要領袖也被稱為神的<em>奴僕</em>或<em>僕人</em>（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh14:7\">書14:7</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:12\">王下18:12</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:23\">結34:23</a>）。</p></li><li><p><em>寫信給那被召……的人</em>：我們不清楚猶大書具體是寫給誰的。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "65001001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:1",
          "end_ref": "65001001",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:1"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694418,
    "reference_id": 18832,
    "title": "猶大書 1:1–2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "65001001-65001002",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>猶大按照書信開頭的典型結構，先介紹自己，接著稱呼其讀者，並為他們禱告。</p></li><li><p>為耶穌基督保守的人：這個片語強調了一個重要的觀點（另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:21\">1:21</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:24\">24</a>）。<span>當信徒面對那些傳講關於神的錯誤教導的人時，這樣的說法能賜給他們信心。</span></p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "65001001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:1",
          "end_ref": "65001002",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:2"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694433,
    "reference_id": 18847,
    "title": "猶大書 1:3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "65001003",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>在新約聖經中，「信心」指的通常是相信的行為，而「真道」則是指基督信仰。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "65001003",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:3",
          "end_ref": "65001003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694432,
    "reference_id": 18846,
    "title": "猶大書 1:3–4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "65001003-65001004",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>在新約聖經書信中，此處通常會出現感恩，但猶大在此解釋了他寫信的主要目的（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:8-Rom1:14\">羅1:8–14</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:4-1Cor1:9\">林前1:4–9</a>）。因錯誤的教導對他的讀者的信仰造成了嚴重的威脅（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:22-Jude1:23\">猶1:22–23</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "65001003",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:3",
          "end_ref": "65001004",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:4"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694434,
    "reference_id": 18848,
    "title": "猶大書 1:4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "65001004",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>人們可能會誤解神的奇妙恩典，認為有了恩典我們就能做錯誤的事（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:1-Rom6:23\">羅6章</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "65001004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:4",
          "end_ref": "65001004",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:4"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694436,
    "reference_id": 18850,
    "title": "猶大書 1:5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "65001005",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>耶穌在降生於世上之前就已存在，並救了以色列百姓出埃及。後來，祂刑罰了那些不信的人（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:4\">林前10:4</a>）。</p></li><li><p><em>主救了他的百姓出埃及地，後來就把那些不信的滅絕了：</em>多數人不相信神會保護他們。因為他們的不信，神讓那一代人（除了約書亞和迦勒）在曠野漂流直到他們滅亡（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:1-Num14:45\">民14章</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "65001005",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:5",
          "end_ref": "65001005",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:5"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694435,
    "reference_id": 18849,
    "title": "猶大書 1:5–16",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "65001005-65001016",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>這個段落使用舊約聖經中神審判假教師的例子，來解釋在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:4\">一章4節</a>中「自古被定受刑罰的」這句話的意義。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "65001005",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:5",
          "end_ref": "65001016",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:16"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694437,
    "reference_id": 18851,
    "title": "猶大書 1:6",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "65001006",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>此處的天使指的可能是撒但及跟隨牠墮落的天使，但沒有舊約聖經經文明確地描述這一事件（見<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"15042\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotes\">賽14:12–17</span>；<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"10823\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotes\">結28:12–19</span>的研讀註釋）。而猶大指的可能是<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:1-Gen6:4\">創世記六章1至4節</a>。猶太傳統將<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:1-Gen6:22\">創世記第六章</a>中的「神的兒子們」理解為邪惡的天使。他們相信神因為他們與女人發生了性關係而刑罰了這些天使（見<em>以諾一書</em>〔<em>1&nbsp;Enoch</em>〕6–10；另見<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"14924\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotes\">彼前3:19–20；</span><span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"13973\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotes\">彼後2:4</span>的研讀註釋）。猶大後來（在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:14-Jude1:15\">第14–15節</a>）直接引用了<em>以諾一書</em>。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "65001006",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:6",
          "end_ref": "65001006",
