  {
    "content_id": 694438,
    "reference_id": 18852,
    "title": "猶大書 1:7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "65001007",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>神對所多瑪和蛾摩拉的審判眾所周知（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:17-Gen19:26\">創18:17–19:26</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:26-Luke17:29\">路17:26–29</a>）。</p></li><li><p><em>周圍城邑</em>：<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut29:23\">申命記二十九章23節</a>中提到的押瑪和洗扁。</p></li><li><p><em>一味地行淫，隨從逆性的情慾</em>：這指的可能是同性之間的性關係 （<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen19:5-Gen19:10\">創19:5–10</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "65001007",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:7",
          "end_ref": "65001007",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:7"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694439,
    "reference_id": 18853,
    "title": "猶大書 1:8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "65001008",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><em>在尊位的</em>：這指的可能是墮落的天使。在舊約聖經和猶太教中，天使在審判中扮演重要的角色。假教師可能是在淡化未來審判的事實（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:18\">1:18</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:3-2Pet3:4\">彼後3:3–4</a>）或否認這些抵擋神的天使有尊貴的起源（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:10\">彼後2:10</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "65001008",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:8",
          "end_ref": "65001008",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:8"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694440,
    "reference_id": 18854,
    "title": "猶大書 1:9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "65001009",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>米迦勒是最有能力的天使之一。在猶太傳統中，「天使長」是最高級別的天使（另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:16\">帖前4:16</a>）。米迦勒在聖經中被多次提及（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan10:13\">但10:13</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan10:21\">21</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:1\">12:1</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:7\">啟12:7</a>）。他與魔鬼爭辯摩西屍首的故事並不在舊約聖經中，但在猶太傳統文獻中可以找到（見<em>摩西升天記</em>〔<em>Assumption of Moses</em>〕）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "65001009",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:9",
          "end_ref": "65001009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694419,
    "reference_id": 18833,
    "title": "猶大書 1:11",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "65001011",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p><em>該隱</em>：參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:1-Gen4:16\">創世記四章1至16節</a>。</p></li><li><p><em>巴蘭</em>：參<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"13964\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotes\">彼得後書二章15節的研讀註釋</span>。</p></li><li><p><em>可拉</em>：參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:1-Num16:35\">民數記十六章1至35節</a>。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "65001011",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:11",
          "end_ref": "65001011",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:11"
        }
      ],
