  {
    "content_id": 694420,
    "reference_id": 18834,
    "title": "猶大書 1:12",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "65001012",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>初代基督徒將慶祝聖餐作為共享團契筵席的一部分。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "65001012",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:12",
          "end_ref": "65001012",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:12"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694421,
    "reference_id": 18835,
    "title": "猶大書 1:13",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "65001013",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>人們曾經認為行星是流蕩的星，因為它們在天空中以不規則的軌跡運行。同樣地，假教師也在流蕩（因為他們教授虛假的教導），而神譴責他們的行為。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "65001013",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:13",
          "end_ref": "65001013",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:13"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694422,
    "reference_id": 18836,
    "title": "猶大書 1:14–15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "65001014-65001015",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>以諾是亞當較早期的後裔（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen5:18-Gen5:24\">創5:18–24</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr1:3\">代上1:3</a>）。<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen5:24\">創世記五章24節</a>中表明以諾沒有經歷死亡，而是直接被接到天上（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs2:1-2Kgs2:13\">王下2:1–13</a>；見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:5\">來11:5</a>）。這種來自神的特殊認可，以及他在聖經中被提及的次數有限，使以諾成為一個有趣的人物。猶太文學中包含許多關於他的傳說，<span>並且有至少兩本介於舊約聖經與新約聖經之間因他所寫的啟示異象書</span>（<em>以諾一書、二書</em>〔<em>1–2 Enoch</em>〕）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "65001014",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:14",
          "end_ref": "65001015",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:15"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694424,
    "reference_id": 18838,
    "title": "猶大書 1:17",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "65001017",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><em>我們主耶穌基督之使徒從前所說的話</em>：見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:29-Acts20:30\">使徒行傳二十章29至30節</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:1-1Tim4:3\">提摩太前書四章1至3節</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:1-2Tim3:5\">提摩太後書三章1至5節</a>。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "65001017",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:17",
          "end_ref": "65001017",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:17"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694423,
    "reference_id": 18837,
    "title": "猶大書 1:17–23",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "65001017-65001023",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>在責備假教師之後，猶大再次直接勉勵他的讀者（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:3-Jude1:4\">1:3–4</a>）。使徒曾警告他們關於錯誤的教導的問題（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:17-Jude1:19\">1:17–19</a>）。他們應該在信仰上互相扶持（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:20-Jude1:21\">1:20–21</a>）。他們應該要幫助那些可能被假教師誤導的人（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:22-Jude1:23\">1:22–23</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "65001017",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:17",
          "end_ref": "65001023",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:23"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694425,
    "reference_id": 18839,
    "title": "猶大書 1:18",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "65001018",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><em>末世</em>：耶穌作為彌賽亞（神所揀選的那位）降臨，開啟了神的計劃的最後階段。這是舊約聖經中關於末後日子的預言開始成就的時刻。因此，猶大引用使徒的預言來應對由假教師在當時所引發的危機（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:19\">1:19</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "65001018",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:18",
          "end_ref": "65001018",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:18"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694427,
    "reference_id": 18841,
    "title": "猶大書 1:20",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "65001020",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><em>至聖的真道</em>：如同<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:3\">一章3節</a>中所提及的，<em>真道</em>指的是基督徒所相信的基本教義。這些教義包括基督徒應該如何看待神以及如何生活。假教師危害到這些信仰，因此信徒必須持守它們。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "65001020",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:20",
          "end_ref": "65001020",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JUD 1:20"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694429,
    "reference_id": 18843,
    "title": "猶大書 1:22",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "65001022",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><em>有些人存疑心</em>：一些信徒因假教師的言論而開始懷疑自己的信仰。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
